title: SUNDAY SERMON: How to Profit From Your Past, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO261
itunes:title: SUNDAY SERMON: How to Profit From Your Past, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO261
description: It seems like everyday I get somebody emailing me or messaging me complaining or beating themselves up about something they said or did in the past. Part of me gets that, but most of me doesn't. Complaining about the past is illogical. Beating yourself up about your past is pointless. Instead, you should be using your past to benefit your present & your future. How do the happiest, most satisfied people do that? That’s what we talk about in today’s Sunday Sermon.
